Author: polymerium
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ⚡ ArmPack ⚡
Body: Hello, on each package of the product there is a one-time code that is chroned in our blockchain. The code has all the information about the product, release date, expiration date, supply chain, etc. Using the application of ArmWallet, the buyer checks the code and verifies that the product is original. Codes can not be faked. For product verification, the buyer receives bonuses from the manufacturer in ArmCoin or in his tokens. This will not only save the world from fakes, but also save lives - for example, forgery of medicines will stop. Manufacturers will be able to make unique marketing through the application of ArmWallet and target advertising to the maximum desired audience (choose preferences, monthly expenses, geo-position, etc.).

Author: polymerium
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ⚡ ArmPack ⚡
Body: Franchising will be launched, so that we can build an extensive network of representative offices and attract manufacturers very quickly.

Author: polymerium
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ⚡ ArmPack ⚡
Body: We will have a program for other countries, which will enable representatives to connect local brands to the system. Developers are not only from Russia. Producers will pay for codes the lowest price in the world (0,01$). The main income will be formed from the marketing capabilities of the platform. Brands / manufacturers will pay only in tokens, we have come up with how to make the purchase of tokens for brands very simple and legal. We canceled the bounty company, because we do not want the bounty members to collapse the capitalization of ArmCoin when listing on the stock exchange. We have already received preliminary approval from the stock exchange from the TOP 15.

Author: polymerium
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ⚡ ArmPack ⚡
Body: We decided not to do a test version in a centralized form, but to start developing a decentralized system immediately. This requires more time, at the moment the readiness is 30%. To attract additional developers, we have already announced a hackathon, and have already received more than 50 requests for participation.

Author: polymerium
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ⚡ ArmPack ⚡
Body: Yes, right. We make the lowest price in the world, only $ 0.01 per code. We are not going to earn selling codes. The main revenue is the marketing capabilities of the platform. Imagine that all buyers / customers of all connected brands will become users of our application ArmWallet. Ie we do not pay anything for downloading our application, and we get a huge number of buyers / customers from brands. For example, one dairy producer can give us more than 500,000 downloads of our application. And there will be a lot of such brands / producers.
